snippet.title: Zelle trailer
snippet.description:
Zelle is a occult adventure game for PC/Mac. 
You can explore the inside and outside of the castle using adventure game mechanics and battle demons with strategic mouse clicks.
This game will be released Oct 2019.

steam page: https://store.steampowered.com/app/725330/Zelle/
